<topic id="features">
    <title>Features</title>
    <shortdesc>Key features of this plugin test project.</shortdesc>
    <body>
        <section>
            <title>Automatic Setup</title>
            <ul>
                <li>Downloads DITA-OT automatically from GitHub releases</li>
                <li>Installs plugins from the official DITA-OT registry</li>
                <li>Skips download/install if already present (incremental builds)</li>
                <li>Cross-platform support (Windows, macOS, Linux)</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <title>Flexible Configuration</title>
            <ul>
                <li>Configurable DITA-OT version</li>
                <li>Configurable plugin selection</li>
                <li>Configurable transformation type</li>
                <li>Override via command line or properties file</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <title>Output Verification</title>
            <ul>
                <li>Automatic verification of generated files</li>
                <li>File type checking based on transtype</li>
                <li>Detailed output reporting</li>
                <li>Fail-fast on errors</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <title>Integration with Gradle</title>
            <ul>
                <li>Full Gradle lifecycle integration</li>
                <li>Incremental build support</li>
                <li>Task caching</li>
                <li>Parallel execution support</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </body>
</topic>
